General.Name: Jiangsu Junxia Gym Equipment Co. Ltd. A
General.Description: Jiangsu Junxia Gym Equipment Co., Ltd manufactures and sells sporting goods and fitness equipment in China. It offers aerobic fitness equipment, such as treadmills, exercise bikes, magnetic cars, elliptical machines, and rowing machines; strength fitness equipment, including machines, smith trainers, gantries, single parallel bars, and weightlifting beds; and vertical squat trainers, triceps training devices, iso-stretch back and swivel training devices, low pull trainers, horizontal leg bend trainers, leg extension trainers, kick trainers, hips compound training devices, thigh extension training devices, standing calf trainers, butterfly machines, straight arm clip chest training devices, seated chest push trainers, shoulder press training devices, and push shoulder chairs. The company also provides T-shaped rowing trainers, dumbbell flat benches, adjustable abdominal muscle plates and dumbbell chairs, stretching machines, double dumbbell racks, adjustable roman stools, incline and decline bench presses, flat bench presses, high tensile training devices, reverse pedal machines, abdominal flexion training devices, leg bending exercisers, leg bending training devices, seated rowing trainers, seated calf trainers, biceps training chairs, comprehensive shelf equipment, barbell racks, squat racks, and bar knee lifters. In addition, it offers triple horizontal bars, hand and leg massagers, leg presses, buried basketball hoops, mobile basketball hoops, outdoor table tennis tables, and combination trainers; rehabilitation equipment, such as abdominal muscle training devices, waist training devices, butterfly clip chest/butterfly chest expansion trainers, and seated chest push/pull back trainers; and other small fitness equipment. The company exports its products to approximately 20 countries and regions, including the United States, Europe, and Australia. Jiangsu Junxia Gym Equipment Co., Ltd was founded in 1973 and is based in Xuzhou, China.
